A service where job seekers can post resumes and search job listings and where employers can search resumes and post job listings.

The site lists its mission is to foster the Bitcoin ecosystem with the latest technologies in hopes of creating a larger Open Virtual Market for a more Social and Rich Internet for the future.

The site can be cutomized to store Searches and Jobs. 

